533
00:43:59,471 --> 00:44:03,892
My uncle told me what happened in
the Temple of Sublime Truth 60 years ago.

534
00:44:04,059 --> 00:44:06,102
When you became the next
and protected him,

535
00:44:06,186 --> 00:44:07,979
