– The air.

595
00:49:09,489 --> 00:49:12,325
You can't see it, but it fills your lungs.

596
00:49:15,537 --> 00:49:19,707
It's as real as blood or flesh or bone

597
00:49:19,749 --> 00:49:21,751
or earth, or water.

598
00:49:22,377 --> 00:49:26,422
Once you realize this,
you treat the air the same way.

599
00:49:26,506 --> 00:49:29,050
You step on it as you would a stone.

600
00:49:29,843 --> 00:49:32,679
You swim through it as you would the sea.

601
00:49:33,263 --> 00:49:35,723
And all you have to do is believe.

602
00:49:36,141 --> 00:49:37,600
